WEBVTT

00:10.812 --> 00:12.013
<i>Who are they?</i>

00:12.014 --> 00:14.182
<i>Maroons. Escaped slaves.</i>

00:14.183 --> 00:16.050
<i>They must have a camp upriver.</i>

00:16.050 --> 00:17.218
<i>She is everything here.</i>

00:17.219 --> 00:19.354
<i>Priestess, governess, warlord.</i>

00:19.355 --> 00:21.189
<i>She's not to be underestimated.</i>

00:21.190 --> 00:22.393
Spain. What did you
have to promise them?

00:22.394 --> 00:24.392
That I would secure the remains
of the Urca De Lima's gold

00:24.393 --> 00:25.860
<i>and return it to Havana.</i>

00:25.861 --> 00:27.528
<i>You set aside some of the gold?</i>

00:27.529 --> 00:28.729
- She did.
- How much?

00:28.730 --> 00:31.198
- Eh.
- You don't think there's any way

00:31.199 --> 00:33.000
we can challenge that
blockade directly, do you?

00:33.001 --> 00:35.436
<i>We're working on something
to even the odds a bit.</i>

00:35.880 --> 00:37.188
Get her inside!

00:38.562 --> 00:40.508
<i>I wonder if the pardons
are the victory</i>

00:40.509 --> 00:43.443
<i>and that the most enlightened
thing that I can do</i>

00:43.444 --> 00:45.678
is let this be the end
of Captain Flint.

00:45.679 --> 00:47.881
The pirates must be eliminated.

00:47.882 --> 00:49.349
<i>Why not consult Father?</i>

00:49.350 --> 00:51.551
Your father aids us
from his position in Nassau.

00:51.552 --> 00:54.587
- Please, come with me.
- Lower your weapons. Now!

00:54.588 --> 00:55.789
No, no! No!

